Invocation Name: game of thrones quotes
des:
This skill features a realm of various quotes from Game of Thrones. Simply ask Alexa to give you a quote from Game of Thrones and it will provide you with a random quote from one of the characters in the show or a quote/motto from one of the Houses in Game of Thrones. This skill is filled with quotes from all seasons so far. Enjoy! Winter is Here!

I made this as a fan of Game of Thrones. I'm not officially associated with Game of Thrones, George RR Martin, or HBO.

(Game of Thrones is for mature audiences only, and this skill includes some mature quotes from the show.)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
